      • LexicalScope.TempManager

        protected LexicalScope.TempManager(LexicalScope.TempManager tempManager)
        Construct a TempManager which can be merged back into the supplied tempManager. This basically means that the temp numbering will never overlap.
        Parameters:
        tempManager - the TempManager which this tempManager may be merged into
